About Us
Florida is full of beautiful locations and fun activities, making it difficult to pinpoint the best area to build your retirement. Just remember, the one thing that sets any retirement community apart from another is the company behind the community. CRF Communities has been providing 55+ adults with numerous lifestyle options at affordable prices for over 40 years. Family-owned and operated, CRF Resales offers 15 distinct Central Florida locations from which to choose. The owner and employee’s dedication to providing quality service and products should be significant in this exciting decision-making process. This unbelievable selection and unmatched commitment to excellence assure that you can find your dream Florida retirement with CRF.
Quality and affordability are attributes CRF strives to provide to all current and future residents. Manufactured homes continue to be the perfect way to accomplish both. Previously owned homes ranging from $5,000 to $150,000 have been constructed and maintained according to strict building codes and CRF’s high standards. This home style allows you to have a fantastic location and lifestyle while remaining within a comfortable budget. You are sure to receive an exceptional value without sacrificing your dream Florida retirement.
As a company, we also showcase “
featured homes
” throughout the year. These homes are hand-selected and allow you to enjoy reduced sale prices and lot rents! These two things combined can often be the little bit of grace you need when beginning your retirement, and we are happy to present them to you in our
weekly emailed newsletter!
See first-hand why CRF Communities has been a leader in Central Florida Retirement and bringing life to thousands of dreams like yours for over four decades.
Our knowledgeable staff is here to help. Feel free to call us; we would love to speak with you:
866-370-1581
. Not ready for a conversation? Click a button to the right for more details, or sign up to receive our
weekly emailed newsletter
by clicking the button below.
We look forward to helping you find your place in the Sunshine State!
